Documentation for 'swindle/swindle.ss'

This module combines all modules to form the Swindle language module.

Note that it does not re-define '#%module-begin', so the language used for transformers is still the one defined by 'turbo'.

This module exports bindings from: 'mzlib/turbo', 'mzlib/clos', 'mzlib/extra'. It is intended to be used as a language module (as an initial-import for other modules).
